<div class="user-container">
    <h1>My Profile</h1>
    <img class="ghosts" src="/imgs/red-ghost.png" alt="Red Ghost">
    {{!-- Need to specify created_at in the routes --}}
    <h2>You've been a registered player with us since {{format_date created_at}}</h2>

    <div class="info-container">
        <h2>Username: {{user-container}}</h2>
        {{!-- Need to figure out how to hide password --}}
        <h2>Password: {{password}}</h2>
        <img class="password" src="/imgs/green-x.png" alt="Green 'X'"> 
        {{!-- On click, reveal passowrd --}}
    </div>

    <div class="logout">
        <p>Logout</p>  
        <img class="logout-btn" src="/imgs/logout.png" alt="Yellow 'Game Over'"> 
    </div>

    <div class="delete-player">
        <p>Delete My Profile</p>
        <img class="delete-btn" src="/imgs/terminate.png" alt="Red 'Terminate Player'"> 
    </div>

    {{!-- The Modal --}}
    <div id="clearModal" class="modal">
      {{!-- Modal content --}}
      <div class="modal-content">
        <p>Whoah whoah whoah. If you proceed, you're gonna delete your player profile, and all of your saved games. You sure you're ready for that level of commitment?</p>
        <div class="yes-no">
          <img id="no" class="btn" src="/imgs/yello-b.png"><p>Oh whoops. Never mind.</p> <img id="yes" class="btn" src="/imgs/red-a.png"><p>I know what I'm about, son.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
        
    
</div>
<img class="not-tetris" src="/imgs/tetris.png" alt="Colorful shapes">

{{!-- {{#if logged_in}} --}}
<script src="/js/logout.js"></script>
<script src="/js/delete.js"></script>
{{!-- {{/if}} --}}